# .manim Language Server — Haxe to JS build configuration
# Compiles MacroManimParser + LSP server to a single Node.js script.
#
# Build: haxe lsp/lsp-server.hxml
# Run:   node lsp/bin/server.js

-cp lsp/src
-cp src

-main manim.lsp.ManimLanguageServer
-js lsp/bin/server.js

# Exclude Heaps/HashLink dependencies (parser-only mode)
-D noheaps

# Disable position tracking in AST (not needed for LSP, saves output size)
# -D MULTIANIM_TRACE
